metadata.name: Bullrun Bulldogs #1
metadata.description: The "Bullrun Bulldogs" are a fun and diverse group, but they all have two things in common...their love of chicken nuggets and finding new ways to invest in crypto!  Always finding new ways to have fun, you'll find them at arcades, playing in bands, brushing up on their martial arts skills, and sometimes you'll even find them enjoying slow paced coffee shops.  From nerds, to goofs, weirdos, to stiffs, we all probably have something in common with the Bullrun Bulldogs.
